statements: SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations WHERE land_use_category = 'Residential';
SELECT id, zoning_code FROM zoning_regulations WHERE maximum_building_height > 50;
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations WHERE setback_requirement < 10;
SELECT id, zoning_code, maximum_building_height FROM zoning_regulations ORDER BY maximum_building_height DESC;
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations WHERE land_use_category = 'Commercial' ORDER BY setback_requirement ASC;
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations WHERE maximum_building_height > 10 AND setback_requirement < 50 ORDER BY land_use_category DESC
SELECT id, zoning_code, maximum_building_height FROM zoning_regulations WHERE maximum_building_height BETWEEN 20 AND 30 AND land_use_category = 'Residential' ORDER BY id ASC
SELECT zoning_code, MAX(maximum_building_height), MIN(setback_requirement) FROM zoning_regulations WHERE land_use_category = 'Commercial' GROUP BY zoning_code ORDER BY maximum_building_height DESC
SELECT id, land_use_category, zoning_code, maximum_building_height + setback_requirement AS total_building_space FROM zoning_regulations WHERE maximum_building_height > setback_requirement
SELECT id, zoning_code, zoning_code AS alias_code FROM zoning_regulations WHERE zoning_code IS NOT NULL
SELECT * FROM land_use_regulations;
SELECT id, zone_id, land_use_type FROM land_use_regulations WHERE zone_id = 5;
SELECT district_name, total_area FROM zoning_districts WHERE residential_density > 50 ORDER BY total_area DESC;
SELECT id, land_use_type FROM land_use_regulations WHERE restrictions IS NOT NULL;
SELECT zone_id, district_name, residential_density FROM zoning_districts WHERE total_area < 1000;
SELECT * FROM land_use_regulations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT land_use_type, restrictions FROM land_use_regulations WHERE zone_id = 3 ORDER BY land_use_type DESC, id ASC;
SELECT zone_id, district_name, total_area FROM zoning_districts WHERE residential_density > 500 ORDER BY district_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM zoning_districts WHERE total_area < 10000;
SELECT district_name, total_area, residential_density FROM zoning_districts WHERE residential_density BETWEEN 200 AND 600 ORDER BY total_area DESC;
SELECT * FROM land_use_zones;
SELECT zone_id, zone_name FROM land_use_zones ORDER BY zone_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM zoning_restrictions WHERE restriction_type = 'Residential';
SELECT zone_id, zone_description FROM land_use_zones WHERE zone_id = 3;
SELECT property_id, zone_id, restriction_id FROM property_zoning LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM land_use_zones;
SELECT zone_name, zone_description FROM land_use_zones ORDER BY zone_id DESC;
SELECT property_id, restriction_type, restriction_description FROM property_zoning JOIN zoning_restrictions ON property_zoning.restriction_id=zoning_restrictions.restriction_id;
SELECT zone_id, COUNT(*) AS total_properties FROM property_zoning GROUP BY zone_id ORDER BY total_properties DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_zoning WHERE zone_id IN (SELECT zone_id FROM land_use_zones WHERE zone_name='Residential');
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations;
SELECT zone_name, building_height FROM zoning_regulations WHERE building_height > 50;
SELECT * FROM permitted_uses ORDER BY land_use_category_id DESC;
SELECT zone_id, parcel_id FROM zoning_map WHERE zone_id = 3;
SELECT category_name, description FROM land_use_categories WHERE ID = 2;
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations ORDER BY zone_name ASC, building_height DESC;
SELECT zone_name, building_height, setback_distance FROM zoning_regulations WHERE building_height > 50 AND setback_distance < 10;
SELECT zone_name, COUNT(*) FROM zoning_map GROUP BY zone_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 2 ORDER BY zone_id;

SELECT pr.parcel_id, zr.zone_name, lr.category_name FROM permitted_uses pu JOIN zoning_map zm ON pu.zone_id = zm.zone_id JOIN zoning_regulations zr ON zm.zone_id = zr.ID JOIN land_use_categories lr ON pu.land_use_category_id = lr.ID WHERE pu.land_use_category_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY pr.parcel_id ASC;
SELECT lr.category_name, COUNT(*) FROM permitted_uses pu JOIN land_use_categories lr ON pu.land_use_category_id = lr.ID GROUP BY lr.category_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 0 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations;
SELECT zone_name, land_use_type FROM zoning_regulations WHERE height_limit > 100;
SELECT zone_name, setback_distance FROM zoning_regulations WHERE zone_name = 'Residential';
SELECT * FROM parcel_information WHERE parcel_size < 5000;
SELECT inspector_name, inspection_date FROM inspector_records ORDER BY inspection_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM zoning_regulations LIMIT 5;
SELECT zone_name, land_use_type, height_limit FROM zoning_regulations WHERE height_limit > 5 ORDER BY height_limit DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM parcel_information JOIN zoning_regulations ON parcel_information.zone_id = zoning_regulations.id WHERE parcel_size > 100 ORDER BY zone_name, parcel_size DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT building_permits.permit_id, permit_date, permit_type, parcel_size FROM building_permits JOIN parcel_information ON building_permits.parcel_id = parcel_information.parcel_id WHERE permit_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY parcel_size LIMIT 5;

SELECT inspector_id, inspector_name, inspection_date, violation_description FROM inspector_records JOIN violation_records ON inspector_records.violation_id = violation_records.violation_id WHERE inspection_date < '2022-06-01' ORDER BY inspection_date DESC LIMIT 5;
